239
00:13:50,830 --> 00:13:52,205
Fine, I'll change.

240
00:13:53,999 --> 00:13:55,917
<font color="#E86CE4">(WHIP CRACKS ON PHONE)</font>

241
00:14:00,381 --> 00:14:01,422
<font color="#E86CE4">(CACKLES)</font>

242
00:14:05,970 --> 00:14:07,637
I don't think I wanna play a game.

243
00:14:07,805 --> 00:14:10,473
They're playing one across the hall.
We should too.

244
00:14:10,641 --> 00:14:14,352
Okay, we are gonna take turns
bouncing a quarter off the table.

245
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:17,188
