248
00:14:27,199 --> 00:14:29,868
So now I will drink this entire cup of beer...

249
00:14:30,035 --> 00:14:33,037
...and you will go again and we can...

250
00:14:36,500 --> 00:14:39,711
All right, so, yeah.
